433 Sense of Space
==================

This folder contains a mixed-license firmware project. The compiled UF2 files and
raw audio assets are not distributed under a single open-source license because
they include third-party audio with different terms.

Embedded BBC Sound Effects Audio
--------------------------------

The ambience loop assets:

- `433_loop_10k_s8_stereo.bin`
- `433_loop_12k_s8_stereo.bin`
- `433_loop_24k_s16_stereo.bin`
- the UF2 firmware images that embed those assets

are derived from BBC Sound Effects Archive item `07003043`
(`bbc_theatres--_07003043`).

BBC Sound Effects Archive audio is subject to the BBC Sound Effects Archive
licensing terms:

https://sound-effects.bbcrewind.co.uk/licensing

These embedded BBC-derived assets are included here only for non-commercial,
personal, or research purposes unless separately licensed from the BBC. Public,
commercial, broadcast, product, or other uses outside those terms require checking
the BBC licence terms and, where needed, obtaining a separate BBC licence.

Seat Creak Audio
----------------

The seat creak asset:

- `seat_creak_12k_s8_stereo.bin`

is derived from:

- `Chair creaking back and forth 01.wav`
- Creator: `unkleceeg`
- URL: https://freesound.org/people/unkleceeg/sounds/276473/
- Licence: Creative Commons 0 / Public Domain Dedication

See `SEAT_CREAK_SOURCE.md` for the exact source notes and conversion details.

Firmware Source Code
--------------------

New project-specific source code in this folder may be used, modified, and shared
for non-commercial, personal, or research use together with the embedded audio
assets described above.

Some source files are copied or adapted from existing Music Thing Modular Workshop
Computer / Pico SDK project material and retain their original notices and licence
status where applicable, including:

- `ComputerCard.h`
- `pico_sdk_import.cmake`
- `reverb_dsp.c`
- `reverb_dsp.h`

No additional permission is granted here for the BBC-derived audio beyond the BBC
Sound Effects Archive terms.
